[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man suffers burns in Broxburn house blaze

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man was taken to hospital for treatment following a fire at a house in West Lothian.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 35-year-old suffered burns after the fire broke out in a property in East Main Street in Broxburn.
The Scottish Fire and Rescue Service attended the blaze after being alerted at 01:05 on Saturday.
